{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2018/july","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"hacker-email-alias\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hacker-email-alias\" aria-label=\"hacker email alias permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hacker Email Alias</h3>\n<p>All hackers now have an <a href=\"/hackers/hacker-email-alias.html\">email alias</a> that forwards emails to the email address theyâ€™ve registered with on HackerOne. This provides an easy way for programs to contact you in order to share credentials and information without having to access your actual email address.</p>\n<h3 id=\"sort-notifications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sort-notifications\" aria-label=\"sort notifications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sort Notifications</h3>\n<p>You can now sort notifications from oldest to newest and vice versa.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 379px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"july_2018_sort_notifications\"\n        title=\"july_2018_sort_notifications\"\n        src=\"/static/7fe1fccccde3cbb4724134f75b220b21/811d1/July_2018_notifications_sort.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7fe1fccccde3cbb4724134f75b220b21/fac75/July_2018_notifications_sort.png 125w,\n/static/7fe1fccccde3cbb4724134f75b220b21/63868/July_2018_notifications_sort.png 250w,\n/static/7fe1fccccde3cbb4724134f75b220b21/811d1/July_2018_notifications_sort.png 379w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 379px) 100vw, 379px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hacktivity-redesign\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hacktivity-redesign\" aria-label=\"hacktivity redesign permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hacktivity Redesign</h3>\n<p>We've revamped the look of our <a href=\"https://hackerone.com/hacktivity\">Hacktivity</a> feed so that it has a sleeker design. We've also deprecated the <b>Top</b> tab on Hacktivity.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; displ